This project is a Rust rewrite of dev-machine-guard, originally created by
StepSecurity Inc. and licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Original project: https://github.com/step-security/dev-machine-guard
Original copyright: Copyright 2025 StepSecurity Inc.

This derivative work extends the original with:
- Linux platform support
- Cloud credential detection (AWS, GCP, Azure)
- Container tool detection (Docker, Podman, etc.)
- SSH key auditing with passphrase detection
- Shell config scanning for AI-related environment variables
- Notebook server detection (Jupyter, Marimo)
- Additional AI tool and framework detections
